txt.en: 'The King should have heeded Gimli's warnings....'
'I am sorry, [placeholder], but my duty is to my King...'
'To think that Mistress Zôreth treated us better....'
'I fight you to the death, [placeholder]. Do what you must!'
'How can the King not see? The Ring is cursed!'
'King Váskmun should have killed you! I told him not to let you go free!'
'Oh, the promise of a full belly...'
'I shall join Gimli's folk, but first I must mourn my own...'
'You're too late! The King leads his army across Dor Amarth even now!'
'What has become of my folk? These Firehorns are no kin of mine!'
'It wasn't supposed to end like this...'
'Come back to steal the King's mithril, have you? I think not!'
